ModMetaData.name: Increased Forest Density - Deadly Version V3.0 A16
ModMetaData.author: Helpful Bot
ModMetaData.description: Increases vegetation and trees significantly; new and unique terrain generation. Increases vegetation graphical size. Increases and alters predator presence. Strengthens predators and large mammals considerably; Alters the leather of some stronger animals in terms of comfort and beauty (to a max of 30% which is almost negligible compared to the effect of build quality)
